@CK|cp|8|at| ^*BJ^*N|cp||at| 10 5 4 |AT|^k(J)
@SK|cp|8|at| ^*B10^*N|cp||at| 9 5 4 |AT|^k(10)
@SQ|cp|8|at| ^*B10^*N|cp||at| 9 5 4 |AT|^k(10)|
PG| ***** 30 ***** |


at|
^B@2^Y@3Any other honor combination requires different treatment. A holding of A 9 8 3 2 or of Q J 8 3 2, for example, requires the lead of a low card rather than a high card, and comes under the classification of a length lead.|
PG| ***** 31 ***** |


