The top card of three little ones of Partner's suit should be preferred to the lead of Jack from Jack-Ten in some other suit, and should also be preferred to almost any other length lead. If you have only a doubleton or singleton in partner's suit - well, a point is now reached when so many other factors, psychological and otherwise, enter into the situation that it is best, temporarily, to duck the subject.|
